Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:55.04,OP-JP-8-白,NTP,0,0,0,,Blast away！(Someone there to heal me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.34,OP-JP-8-白,NTP,0,0,0,,重なり合う度に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:02.38,OP-JP-8-白,NTP,0,0,0,,痛みも涙も全て
